influence of the weak neutral interaction.

114
00:07:44,910 --> 00:07:47,020
The exchange of its intermediate boson,

115
00:07:47,020 --> 00:07:51,040
the Z boson, dominates the total
cross section at these energies, and

116
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:54,670
